      <title>白宮審查哈馬斯對加薩停火提案的回應</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/white-house-reviews-hamas-response-gaza-ceasefire-proposal-2024-05-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[白宮週一表示，正在審查伊斯蘭哈馬斯激進組織對停火和釋放人質提案的回應，同時繼續敦促以色列停止對拉法的地面入侵計畫。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/white-house-reviews-hamas-response-gaza-ceasefire-proposal-2024-05-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 19:07:28 GMT</pubDate>
